				<description>&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;img-fluid &#34;&#xA;            src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-2800x4197.png&#34;&#xA;             srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-576x863.webp 576w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-768x1151.webp 768w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-992x1487.webp 992w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-1200x1799.webp 1200w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-1400x2099.webp 1400w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-2800x4197.webp 2800w&#34; sizes=&#34;100vw&#34; height=&#34;4197&#34; width=&#34;2800&#34; alt=&#34;Featured Image&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction-to-ai-in-google-docs&#34; class=&#34;heading &#34;&gt;Introduction to AI in Google Docs&lt;a href=&#34;#introduction-to-ai-in-google-docs&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;introduction-to-ai-in-google-docs&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-link anchor&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 576 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Google Docs has become an essential tool for individuals and businesses alike, providing a convenient and collaborative way to create and edit documents. Recently, Google introduced a new feature called &amp;ldquo;Gemini&amp;rdquo; which utilizes artificial intelligence (AI) to assist with writing tasks. While this feature can be helpful, some users may find the frequent &amp;ldquo;write with Gemini&amp;rdquo; pop-ups to be annoying and distracting. In this article, we will explore the reasons behind these pop-ups and provide a step-by-step guide on how to turn them off.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
